{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"4879-i-can-make-things","title":"Je sais fabriquer plein de choses!","description":"Les enfants peuvent fabriquer plein de jolies choses. Découvre-les dans ce livre appartenant à la collection « Je grandis », qui comporte quatre titres. ","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sak Untala"],"illustrators":["Tanvee Nabar"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/4879-i-can-make-things"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/709183/size3/68acc59fc68640e3cabffa2a367a7375.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/709183/size6/68acc59fc68640e3cabffa2a367a7375.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10628/size6/f182a1c235e0c8a7a9578f3d63a301d4.jpg","text":"Je suis un grand garçon, maintenant.\nJe sais dessiner et fabriquer plein de choses.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10630/size6/8f4085b833328ebad0bb4c829d6bc3bd.jpg","text":"Je dessine ma mère, qui ne bouge pas.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10631/size6/9a216827141b6e2e9285e866397d659d.jpg","text":"Je dessine ma sœur, qui n'arrête pas de bouger.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10632/size6/3feaf340a7b0144fd6cd477eac36444e.jpg","text":"Je dessine plein de choses.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10633/size6/57aef08a63fdae439e3d9d81f2d5f94c.jpg","text":"Mais je n'ai pas le droit de dessiner sur les murs.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10634/size6/53110634399378d31dd1fe12d51e871a.jpg","text":"Je sais fabriquer plein de choses.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10635/size6/73cd6940cf5301f73dd47e6f6cb05a7d.jpg","text":"Je dessine un chat.\nIl est très gros.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10636/size6/534ba0193961d8a8422ee4cf809b86e3.jpg","text":"Je fabrique un poisson.\nIl est tout petit.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10637/size6/fe3687fb06f0fefba37c63c2b330ca2c.jpg","text":"Je fabrique des bateaux, des oiseaux\net des avions en papier.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10638/size6/47a6a033579def00aaa02baebd79c105.jpg","text":"Je fabrique des maisons et des trains.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10639/size6/d5faf2ebda41b84ac55199ff36d2e935.jpg","text":"Ma sœur fait beaucoup de dégâts!\nJe sais fabriquer plein de choses, mais ma sœur, elle, ne sait pas.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":106}}